history.content:
Hello, I am writing this post to invite you all to the Berkeley Data Science Panel 2017 on Saturday November 18 from 12:30 PM - 6:00 PM, since I believe this is an event that is relevant to many people in this group.

The Berkeley Data Science Panel is the annual data science-related career-driven event at UC Berkeley. This is the 2nd Annual Data Science Career Panel in UC Berkeley hosted by Data Science Society at Berkeley (DSS @ Berkeley) and Machine Learning at Berkeley (ML@B). Our theme for this year is Data Science & Machine Learning in Multimedia and Advertising.

We will bring you 7 leading data scientists from companies like Facebook, Huawei, Baidu, Spotify, and GE digital. These speakers will share their research, insights, and findings. Come for a chance to learn from industry leaders, network with professionals, and share your resume!

Ticket information can be found here: 

https://www.eventbrite.com/e/berkeley-data-science-panel-2017-tickets-39467545491?aff=efbeventtix

Use our promo code specifically for CS students - BERKELEYCS - to check out and get a $10 discount.
